  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section id="book" class="cta-bottom">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>U.S. Cooler walk-in down? Call the branch closest to your restaurant.</h2>
      <p>Same-day in LA, Orange County, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside. Commercial diagnostic $120, waived with repair.</p>
